titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 2608.

action.text: Mr. Rogers (KY) asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.
Considered by unanimous consent. (consideration: CR 9/22/2011 H6410-6411)

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection. (text: CR 9/22/2011 H6410)

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 9/26/2011--Passed Senate without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 2608 (Continuing Appropriations Act, 2012).
